owlSpeak.engine.his

Class Reward

  • java.lang.Object
    • owlSpeak.GenericClass
      • owlSpeak.engine.his.Reward
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<GenericClass>

    public class Reward
extends GenericClass
    This class implements the java class representation of the owl concept of a reward. It is used along with automatic policy optimization techniques to determine the reward value for the executed agenda of the dialogue manager OwlSpeak.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Stefan Ultes <stefan.ultes@uni-ulm.de>
